{
  "video_id": "u84skpKSxFk",
  "title": "Financial Statements - Lecture 1 - Uses and Users",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 10860.0,
      "end_time": 12600.0,
      "text": "Hi, Else here."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 12600.0,
      "end_time": 15190.0,
      "text": "And today we&#39;ll be talking about the users and the users"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 15190.0,
      "end_time": 17820.0,
      "text": "of accounting information."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 17820.0,
      "end_time": 20140.0,
      "text": "What is accounting?"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 20140.0,
      "end_time": 22020.0,
      "text": "Accounting is an information system"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 22020.0,
      "end_time": 24480.0,
      "text": "that identifies and records and organizations"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 24480.0,
      "end_time": 26730.0,
      "text": "transactions and then communicates them"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 26730.0,
      "end_time": 29840.0,
      "text": "to a wide variety of interested users."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 29840.0,
      "end_time": 31980.0,
      "text": "A knowledge of accounting is relevant and useful"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 31980.0,
      "end_time": 34490.0,
      "text": "in whatever career you decide to pursue--"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 34490.0,
      "end_time": 38820.0,
      "text": "be it marketing or financial analyst."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 38820.0,
      "end_time": 41610.0,
      "text": "Every position requires some knowledge of accounting"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 41610.0,
      "end_time": 44760.0,
      "text": "or an understanding of how your actions in your position"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 44760.0,
      "end_time": 46620.0,
      "text": "will affect the business overall--"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 46620.0,
      "end_time": 49050.0,
      "text": "both their profitability and their progress as they"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 49050.0,
      "end_time": 50960.0,
      "text": "move forward."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 50960.0,
      "end_time": 54090.0,
      "text": "You must be able to analyze the information from the past,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 54090.0,
      "end_time": 56030.0,
      "text": "so you can adjust what you do in the future"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 56030.0,
      "end_time": 60440.0,
      "text": "to ensure the company you own or work for is profitable."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 60440.0,
      "end_time": 63140.0,
      "text": "You need accounting information to make informed decisions"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 63140.0,
      "end_time": 66030.0,
      "text": "about how to move forward."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 66030.0,
      "end_time": 68720.0,
      "text": "So just who are the users of financial information"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 68720.0,
      "end_time": 72350.0,
      "text": "and what information do they need to make decisions?"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 72350.0,
      "end_time": 74840.0,
      "text": "Users of accounting information are individuals"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 74840.0,
      "end_time": 77210.0,
      "text": "who have questions about an organization"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 77210.0,
      "end_time": 79640.0,
      "text": "and they need information to find answers and make"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 79640.0,
      "end_time": 81170.0,
      "text": "smart decisions."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 81170.0,
      "end_time": 83000.0,
      "text": "They analyze what happened in the past"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 83000.0,
      "end_time": 86030.0,
      "text": "in order to predict what may happen in the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 86030.0,
      "end_time": 88580.0,
      "text": "To do that, they need detailed accounting information"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 88580.0,
      "end_time": 90440.0,
      "text": "on a timely basis."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 90440.0,
      "end_time": 92030.0,
      "text": "There are really two types of users"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 92030.0,
      "end_time": 96620.0,
      "text": "of accounting information-- internal and external users."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 96620.0,
      "end_time": 100910.0,
      "text": "Internal users plan, organize, and run businesses."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 100910.0,
      "end_time": 103130.0,
      "text": "They ask questions such as what price should"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 103130.0,
      "end_time": 105800.0,
      "text": "we charge for our product or service,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 105800.0,
      "end_time": 109160.0,
      "text": "should we expand on global markets or not,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 109160.0,
      "end_time": 111140.0,
      "text": "what products are profitable, and which"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 111140.0,
      "end_time": 113120.0,
      "text": "should be discontinued?"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 113120.0,
      "end_time": 116300.0,
      "text": "Internal users have access to a large amount of information"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 116300.0,
      "end_time": 120460.0,
      "text": "and they will not be the focus of this course."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 120460.0,
      "end_time": 123490.0,
      "text": "External users are outside of an organization."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 123490.0,
      "end_time": 125470.0,
      "text": "They depend on financial statements"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 125470.0,
      "end_time": 128310.0,
      "text": "in order to make informed decisions."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 128310.0,
      "end_time": 130620.0,
      "text": "Investors, lenders, and other creditors"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 130620.0,
      "end_time": 133920.0,
      "text": "are the key external users of accounting information."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 133920.0,
      "end_time": 136800.0,
      "text": "They make resource allocation decisions."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 136800.0,
      "end_time": 138600.0,
      "text": "That means that their decisions generally"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 138600.0,
      "end_time": 140550.0,
      "text": "involve the giving up or receiving"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 140550.0,
      "end_time": 143920.0,
      "text": "of cash, goods, or services."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 143920.0,
      "end_time": 147330.0,
      "text": "So what questions do the main external users have?"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 147330.0,
      "end_time": 151140.0,
      "text": "Well, an investor might ask if a business is profitable enough"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 151140.0,
      "end_time": 153660.0,
      "text": "to give them a return on their investment."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 153660.0,
      "end_time": 155340.0,
      "text": "A lender might ask if a business will"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 155340.0,
      "end_time": 157830.0,
      "text": "be able to repay a loan plus interest when"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 157830.0,
      "end_time": 159600.0,
      "text": "the loan comes due."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 159600.0,
      "end_time": 161660.0,
      "text": "And other creditors might ask if the bills"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 161660.0,
      "end_time": 165750.0,
      "text": "a company has outstanding will be paid in the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 165750.0,
      "end_time": 169740.0,
      "text": "There are other external users that might also have questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 169740.0,
      "end_time": 172500.0,
      "text": "Employees and labour unions want to know if they will receive"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 172500.0,
      "end_time": 175556.0,
      "text": "higher wages or better benefits."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 175556.0,
      "end_time": 177930.0,
      "text": "Customers are interested in whether a business will honor"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 177930.0,
      "end_time": 180350.0,
      "text": "their warranties in the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 180350.0,
      "end_time": 182510.0,
      "text": "Tax agencies, like Revenue Canada,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 182510.0,
      "end_time": 186380.0,
      "text": "want to know if an organization is paying appropriate taxes."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 186380.0,
      "end_time": 189950.0,
      "text": "Regulatory agencies, like the Securities Exchange Commission,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 189950.0,
      "end_time": 191690.0,
      "text": "want to know if an organization is"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 191690.0,
      "end_time": 194180.0,
      "text": "in compliance with their rules."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 194180.0,
      "end_time": 196250.0,
      "text": "And finally, financial analysts want"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 196250.0,
      "end_time": 198260.0,
      "text": "to know if a company is one that they want"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 198260.0,
      "end_time": 200720.0,
      "text": "to recommend to their clients."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 200720.0,
      "end_time": 203750.0,
      "text": "But the key external users of accounting information"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 203750.0,
      "end_time": 207330.0,
      "text": "are still investors, lenders, and other creditors."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 207330.0,
      "end_time": 208940.0,
      "text": "This is because they are the users who"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 208940.0,
      "end_time": 212112.0,
      "text": "make decisions about resources."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 212112.0,
      "end_time": 214570.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s important to check your understanding and the best way"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 214570.0,
      "end_time": 216460.0,
      "text": "to do that is to test yourself."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 216460.0,
      "end_time": 219160.0,
      "text": "Periodically, you&#39;re going to see multiple choice questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 219160.0,
      "end_time": 221050.0,
      "text": "I recommend that you pause the video"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 221050.0,
      "end_time": 222610.0,
      "text": "and answer the questions yourself"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 222610.0,
      "end_time": 226410.0,
      "text": "before you check to see if you&#39;ve got it right."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 226410.0,
      "end_time": 229470.0,
      "text": "Determining if a company can pay its obligations as they"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 229470.0,
      "end_time": 232157.0,
      "text": "come due is the primary objective of which"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 232157.0,
      "end_time": 233115.0,
      "text": "of the following users?"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 238340.0,
      "end_time": 240830.0,
      "text": "The primary objective of investors, competitors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 240830.0,
      "end_time": 243680.0,
      "text": "and labour unions is not whether a company can pay its bills"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 243680.0,
      "end_time": 245090.0,
      "text": "when they come due."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 245090.0,
      "end_time": 249530.0,
      "text": "Yes, those external users are concerned about that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 249530.0,
      "end_time": 251840.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s not their primary concern."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 251840.0,
      "end_time": 255380.0,
      "text": "Creditors, also called lenders, have a primary objective."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 255380.0,
      "end_time": 257000.0,
      "text": "And that is whether the company is"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 257000.0,
      "end_time": 260310.0,
      "text": "able to pay their bills as they come due."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 260310.0,
      "end_time": 263300.0,
      "text": "What about ethics and accounting information?"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 263300.0,
      "end_time": 265490.0,
      "text": "In order for accounting information to be useful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 265490.0,
      "end_time": 268250.0,
      "text": "it must represent the actual economic activity"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 268250.0,
      "end_time": 269750.0,
      "text": "of an organization--"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 269750.0,
      "end_time": 272620.0,
      "text": "what we call the underlying truth."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 272620.0,
      "end_time": 274250.0,
      "text": "Preparers of accounting information"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 274250.0,
      "end_time": 277550.0,
      "text": "have extensive rules of conduct to guide what they report,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 277550.0,
      "end_time": 279740.0,
      "text": "when they report it, and how they present it"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 279740.0,
      "end_time": 281810.0,
      "text": "to interested users."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 281810.0,
      "end_time": 283910.0,
      "text": "Without ethics in accounting, the information"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 283910.0,
      "end_time": 286280.0,
      "text": "produced by accounting information systems"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 286280.0,
      "end_time": 288590.0,
      "text": "would be useless for decision making."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 288590.0,
      "end_time": 291470.0,
      "text": "Following incorrect information would result in"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 291470.0,
      "end_time": 295010.0,
      "text": "not only possibly a financial crisis, but also"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 295010.0,
      "end_time": 297680.0,
      "text": "reduced confidence in the information provided"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 297680.0,
      "end_time": 299690.0,
      "text": "by accounting systems."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 299690.0,
      "end_time": 301940.0,
      "text": "Ethics and accounting is critical to the health"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 301940.0,
      "end_time": 304610.0,
      "text": "of a business and also financial markets."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 304610.0,
      "end_time": 306170.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s a key focus when preparing"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 306170.0,
      "end_time": 308690.0,
      "text": "accounting information."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 308690.0,
      "end_time": 310430.0,
      "text": "In the next video, we&#39;ll be talking"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 310430.0,
      "end_time": 313310.0,
      "text": "about the three main types of organizations"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 313310.0,
      "end_time": 317290.0,
      "text": "and the main activities that businesses engage in."
    }
  ]
}